{
  "stem": "3022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I went to the-- to a Polish public school for-- for the eighth grade.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the interim, I-- I enrolled in a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I didn't enroll for the ideology.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I enrolled because they had the best soccer field from the other organizations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we played over there, so this was the attraction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Later on, I was exposed to the teaching of this particular-- this was a leftist organization, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was exposed to-- to the teachings of-- of materialism and social structures.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My-- my idea, my plan was to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And many things happened that enforced my desire to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In 1935, our town suffered a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A Jewish innkeeper in a quarrel with one of his customers, accidentally shot the customer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And what happened afterwards is difficult to describe because for over a week, all Jewish homes were closed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Jews wouldn't go out on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The non-Jewish homes displayed pictures of the Holy Mother and crosses and candles so that people who came out as far as 30 miles away on foot to rob, plunder, and-- and kill would know which is a Jewish home, which is not a Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Jewish businesses were destroyed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You couldn't get out of town even if you had a lot of money to pay for-- for-- for transportation to get out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You couldn't get out of town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Police did not intervene.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The gave them free hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were fortunate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "As I said, my mother had a inclination to live in the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We lived in the non-Jewish section.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were the first Jews that moved into this particular section.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
